{"tid":673099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【選舉檢討】居中國港人投票唔使返香港？ 政制局：認真考慮修例","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T08:01:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"339188c3ebd0aef63dcf63d2407abe81f6a91223","tid":673099,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526906499_589d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526906499_589d.png&h=f820db1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人日後隨時變「大灣區人」，建制派對「大灣區人」行使香港憲制權利十分關心，立法會政制及內地事務委員會周一討論選舉安排檢討諮詢報告結果，民建聯李慧琼和經民連梁美芬指出，近年越來越多香港人搬到內地居住，兩人向官員提問，港府是否有措施讓居於內地港人，在選舉時無需回港也可投票。政制及內地事務局副局長陳帥夫表示，根據現行法例，選民必須符合「香港永久性居民」及「通常居港」兩個條件，稱當局會認真考慮是否有需要修改法例，讓居於內地的港人也可「隔空」投票。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員區諾軒則說，便利市民投票措施應全盤考慮，他支持政府不縮短投票時間的做法，因很多巿民現時周日仍上班，若然政府未有替代方案，如讓巿民可提早或在海外投票，便貿然縮短投票時間，將令很多選民失去投票機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180521/58221306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221306&d=06Ej3lOb8dMH8tBioTijC5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=63e24119\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221306&h=b502a0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180521/58221306</a>"},{"pid":"54713e6cac38b96f8d39fe4dc1723425e213bcd3","tid":673099,"uid":7206,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"共產黨做票成本都慳番，唔洗將啲地址轉黎轉去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeb05f05e2299bdb527c0f8dbd482889306f61b","tid":673099,"uid":46527,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"54713e6cac38b96f8d39fe4dc1723425e213bcd3","tid":673099,"uid":7206,"like":49,"